        "feature":"feature init {\n# GSUB feature: Initial Forms\n# Lookups: 1\n\n  script arab; # Arabic\n\n  lookup init_arab {\n  # GSUB lookup 3, type 11 (Single)\n    lookupflag IgnoreMarks RightToLeft;\n    sub @init_medi by @init;\n  } init_arab;\n\n    language SND ; # Sindhi\n    language URD ; # Urdu\n    language KUR ; # Kurdish\n\n} init;\n"
